OL,3,CJustice minister defends civil
OL,4,Cservant's PSNI chief rebuke
OL,6,FIt comes as one of the most senior
OL,7,Fcivil servants in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Faccused the head of the police of
OL,9,Foverstepping the mark in marking the
OL,10,Fpleas for money.
OL,12,FHugh Widdis, permanent secretary at
OL,13,FStormont's Department of Justice, in a
OL,14,Fleaked letter seen by UTV, to the
OL,15,Fchief constable sets out how the chief
OL,16,Fconstable Jon Boutcher ad acted
OL,17,F"outside well-established financial
OL,18,Fprotocols" by writing to Sir Keir
OL,19,FStarmer making the case for more
OL,20,Ffinancial support.
