OL,6,FThe police chief raised those issues
OL,7,Fin his letter to the Prime Minister
OL,8,Fand again in a face-to-face meeting
OL,9,Fwith Sir Keir when he visited a PSNI
OL,10,Ftraining college in Belfast on Monday.
OL,12,FThe Police Federation for Northern
OL,13,FIreland, which represents rank and
OL,14,Ffile officers in the region, reacted
OL,15,Fangrily to the intervention by Mr
OL,16,FWiddis.
