OL,3,CJustice minister defends civil
OL,4,Cservant's PSNI chief rebuke
OL,6,FFederation chair Liam Kelly branded
OL,7,Fthe letter "appalling" and
OL,8,Fcharacterised it as the football
OL,9,Fequivalent of showing the chief
OL,10,Fconstable a yellow card.
OL,12,F"It is unlikely this letter was
OL,13,Fcompiled as a solo run. Mr Widdis
OL,14,Fneeds to clarify who endorsed this
OL,15,Fapproach and explain their collective
OL,16,Fmotivation and intention," he said.
OL,18,F"In my view, the tone and tenor of
OL,19,Fthis letter was disgraceful and was a
OL,20,Fcrude attempt to put the chief
OL,21,Fconstable firmly back in his box.
