OL,6,F"We stand shoulder-to-shoulder with Mr
OL,7,FBoutcher and say loudly to our
OL,8,Fpoliticians, Mr Widdis, and his peers
OL,9,Fto get real around this crisis in
OL,10,Fpolicing rather than resorting to what
OL,11,Fcan only be viewed as coercive tactics
OL,12,Fto curtail, restrain and admonish
OL,13,Fsomeone who is doing his level best
OL,14,Ffor both the service and this entire
OL,15,Fcommunity."
